    <item>
      <title>乌克兰策划袭击，让克里姆林宫失去平衡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-plotted-cross-border-attack-to-throw-kremlin-off-balance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位了解袭击计划的西方官员透露，乌克兰在上周强行越过边境之前，一直在考虑发动袭击的几种可能性，这些袭击将震惊莫斯科领导层，并使总统弗拉基米尔·普京陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-plotted-cross-border-attack-to-throw-kremlin-off-balance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>流动性短缺翻倍 俄罗斯银行争相购买人民币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/russian-banks-scramble-for-yuan-as-liquidity-shortfall-doubles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国加强制裁遏制了人民币流向俄罗斯，迫使当地银行以更高的利率从俄罗斯央行借入货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/russian-banks-scramble-for-yuan-as-liquidity-shortfall-doubles</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 11:11:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰入侵后，俄罗斯军队短缺问题暴露无遗，新一轮征兵风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-kursk-incursion-exposes-russia-troop-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰战争中士兵短缺问题日益严重，俄罗斯不得不提高征兵奖金，以避免再次出现不受欢迎的征兵行动。到目前为止，这一举措似乎没有起到什么作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ukraine-kursk-incursion-exposes-russia-troop-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
